{"tid":652964,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"其實點解零零後會咁鍾意抖音/tik tok?_?","createTime":"2018-05-04T09:25:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-04T17:51:48.000Z","uid":12421,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"588864da07a4fb7a76de322cab53fdae6382a275","tid":652964,"uid":12421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T09:25:13.000Z","msg":"我之前就只聞其名 除咗大陸出 唔清楚個app係做緊乜鳩<br />\n<br />\n咁啱啱就屎忽痕 去down咗個tik tok嚟睇下到底入面係乜鳩嚟 入到去覺得同ig啲即時動態冇乜分別 純粹多咗個bgm <br />\n<br />\n咁就個人觀察呢 絕大部分小學生/初中樣嘅女仔都係香港人嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而佢哋通常都係拍啲手指舞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實都有啲片幾高汁嘅 有啲架仔/jp official channel要溫馨有溫馨 要好笑有好笑<br />\n<br />\n但點解手指舞可以吸引咁多零零後去玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有冇零零後可以入嚟分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff453078d322bab9810b6c3858478c59e071a91e","tid":652964,"uid":12421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T09:32:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"145f808ba224f2ee0f7f0d0058527b907fe13c06","tid":652964,"uid":27416,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T09:37:28.000Z","msg":"70後夠唔明連登有咩好上啦<br />\n唔係咩叫代溝"},{"pid":"84ffa8e1278ce625567b66797dc5c90818e5fb10","tid":652964,"uid":12421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"145f808ba224f2ee0f7f0d0058527b907fe13c06","tid":652964,"uid":27416,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T09:37:28.000Z","msg":"70後夠唔明連登有咩好上啦<br />\n唔係咩叫代溝"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T09:39:18.000Z","msg":"差廿年同差十年都差幾遠下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db2895271129d93c2119ff63cda0596f378dabf9","tid":652964,"uid":43205,"like":6,"dislike